{"tid":370327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"未來數小時天鴿最接近本港　十號信號將維持數小時","createTime":"2017-08-23T03:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T03:41:36.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35da3fd782322d21193b8cd72f7681ca5ff02999","tid":370327,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:03:52.000Z","msg":"十號颶風信號生效，天文台說，未來數小時，強颱風天鴿最接近本港，在香港以南約60公里掠過，預料十號颶風信號會維持數小時。<br />\n<br />\n颶風正影響香港南部地區，隨著天鴿移向珠江口西面，本港將會逐漸轉吹東南風。天文台提醒市民不要離開有屏蔽的地方並留意其破壞性的風力，及可能發生的山泥傾瀉及水浸。<br />\n<br />\n天文台又說，海水上漲可能會引致低窪地區出現嚴重水浸，市民應遠離岸邊及低窪地區。"},{"pid":"7ff99564dd2f48876692e459cfdb9297778ed7e8","tid":370327,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76ae8057ec7c98ac8483de059daababd931c163","tid":370327,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:39:18.000Z","msg":"過15:30就成日放假，加油呀！"},{"pid":"eb6fe037ba042877a0417f6db31efbe4eee7fe34","tid":370327,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:40:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7fc35cac2538cbc3bbaad02ebacd2dcdb108aee","tid":370327,"uid":200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:41:36.000Z","msg":"禾曖鴿鴿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}